<h1>About RRDtool</h1>

#<div style="float:right"><a style="border-width: 0px" href="http://www.oetiker.ch/press"><img src="award-white.png" border="0"/></a></div>

<h2>What RRDtool does</h2>

<p>RRDtool is the OpenSource industry standard, high
performance data logging and graphing system for time series data. RRDtool
can be easily integrated in shell scripts, perl, python, ruby, lua or tcl
applications.</p>

